      "id": 1774533192166,
      "title": "TEST",
      "content": "<span data-teams=\"true\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><blockquote itemtype=\"http://schema.skype.com/Reply\" itemid=\"1773405468130\"><strong itemprop=\"mri\" itemid=\"8:orgid:72e47dd6-bca7-447d-af56-6c6a3a3b64ba\">Jasfer Allen Balboa</strong><span itemprop=\"time\" itemid=\"1773405468130\"></span><p itemprop=\"preview\">Good Morning Tania Crosby, I have claim here with the N864 remark code. Is this claim good to send or not? Please advise, thank you!🙂 Arb ID: 2038892.</p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\"></blockquote><p>Good morning&nbsp;<span itemtype=\"http://schema.skype.com/Mention\" itemid=\"0\">Jasfer</span>, the remark code is for NSA but is a no reply <span itemtype=\"http://schema.skype.com/Mention\" itemid=\"1\">Brooke</span>&nbsp;<span itemtype=\"http://schema.skype.com/Mention\" itemid=\"2\">Clayton</span>&nbsp;please review</p><p></p>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><blockquote itemtype=\"http://schema.skype.com/Reply\" itemid=\"1773405468130\"><strong itemprop=\"mri\" itemid=\"8:orgid:72e47dd6-bca7-447d-af56-6c6a3a3b64ba\">Jasfer Allen Balboa</strong><span itemprop=\"time\" itemid=\"1773405468130\"></span><p itemprop=\"preview\">Good Morning Tania Crosby, I have claim here with the N864 remark code. Is this claim good to send or not? Please advise, thank you!🙂 Arb ID: 2038892.   </p><span itemprop=\"emojis\"><span itemprop=\"smile\" itemid=\"132\" alt=\"🙂\" itemtype=\"false\"></span></span></blockquote><p>Pend for no reply update</p>&nbsp;</span></span>",
